headline: Is It Time To Reassess FedEx (FDX) After Strong Multi Year Share Price Gains?
summary: Many investors are wondering whether FedEx, at around US$304 a share, offers good value today, and are rechecking the numbers to see if the current price still makes sense. The stock’s recent moves, including a 1.2% decline over the last 7 days, a 2.7% gain over 30 days, and returns of 3.9% year to date and 10.7% over 1 year, keep raising questions about what is already priced in after the 76.4% 3 year and 40.1% 5 year returns.
